node.text: PettyWap is an annual pool party produced every July 4th! PettyWap was established in 2018 and has since been an on going success each year... This pool party isn’t open to the public.. it is invite only with a limited amount of persons! “Exclusive Only”!... PettyWap is done in different cities, so far we did New Jersey and Atlanta twice! Stay tuned for the next city! Might be yours! 😈
